data.description: Beautiful 3 Bedroom 1.75 Bath well maintained property with lots of space, covered front patio, 2 living areas a fireplace in one of them, laundry room and a large backyard with patio, utility room that can be used as 4th bedroom or office, solar panels, central to town and easy access to highways, restaurants and shopping centers.
